{"tid":2021183,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"全城願榮光歸香港","createTime":"2020-05-17T14:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-17T16:07:39.000Z","uid":54517,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"10405e5d289098ae74b85181cd2524b75b630fe8","tid":2021183,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:33:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NJRPYFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNJRPYFM.jpg&h=aaa1f8a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國歌法即將殺到埋身，限聚令依然未撤。<br />\n<br />\n但抗爭之心不會就此消滅，唔比聚首，我地就係黃店抗爭，街邊抗爭。Everywhere，都係抗爭之地。<br />\n<br />\n在5月23～5月24號兩日，市民請拿起你的手機，黃店拿出喇叭，大聲放出《願榮光》， 讓榮光響徹街頭小巷。以表我們絕不承認國歌法。<br />\n<br />\n願榮光歸香港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/silverhairgroup/photos/a.845823422463150/1090073364704820/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsilverhairgroup%2Fphotos%2Fa.845823422463150%2F1090073364704820%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCc%2BxtiM4uRDursPVmWLIdz4%3D&h=2351818b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/silverhairgroup/photos/a.845823422463150/1090073364704820/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"c013b9bae080fbc832b257087ef7a19e7e20e02b","tid":2021183,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209d18a93aed99423413f1f2c388c8ef240e4a7e","tid":2021183,"uid":54517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:35:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" 